OL,3,CElection recount announced in St
OL,4,CHelier after close vote
OL,6,FThere will be a full recount of votes
OL,7,Fin the St Helier Central Deputy
OL,8,Fcontest after the initial result was
OL,9,Fjudged to be within the official 1%
OL,10,Fmargin of error.
OL,12,FThere were just 21 votes between
OL,13,FReform Jersey's Lee Carpenter, who was
OL,14,Felected, and the independent candidate
OL,15,FRobin Ward, who missed out.
OL,17,FInitial declared result:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
