OL,3,CElection recount announced in St
OL,4,CHelier after close vote
OL,6,FThe recount will take place at St
OL,7,FHelier Parish Hall from 10am on
OL,8,FWednesday (10 June) and Mr Carpenter
OL,9,Fremains the Deputy-Elect in the
OL,10,Fmeantime.
OL,12,FIn order of votes, the current set of
OL,13,Fresults is:
OL,15,FST HELIER CENTRAL DEPUTY CONTEST
OL,17,FNOT ELECTED
